OpenGL Ubuntu Linux Tutorial
http://www.codeproject.com/Articles/182109/Setting-up-an-OpenGL-development-environment-in-Ub

NOTES:
- This program draws a white square in an FreeGLUT window
- The proper OpenGL compile line for Ubuntu 14.04 is:

	g++ <program_name>.cpp -lGL -lGLU -lglut -o <program_name>
